<div id="deskripsi-singkat-data" class="section level2">
<h2>Deskripsi singkat data</h2>
<p>Ask a home buyer to describe their dream house, and they probably won’t begin with the height of the basement ceiling or the proximity to an east-west railroad. But this playground competition’s dataset proves that much more influences price negotiations than the number of bedrooms or a white-picket fence.</p>
<p>With 79 explanatory variables describing (almost) every aspect of residential homes in Ames, Iowa, this competition challenges you to predict the final price of each home.</p>
<p>data ini bisa diperoleh di link berikut ini</p>
<p><a href="https://drive.google.com/drive/u/2/folders/1TNlpMfcAWHOY2RcUWutMZ4QXgr5NKv8b">Data House Price</a></p>
</div>

<p>Berdasarkan informasi diatas, kita tahu terdata beberapa kolom yang memiliki missing value. Namun hanya 5 kolom saja yang mengalami banyak missing value yaitu <code>Alley</code>,<code>FireplaceQu</code>,<code>PoolQX</code>,<code>Fence</code>,<code>MiscFeature</code>.</p>
<ol start="3" style="list-style-type: decimal">
<li>Menangani Missing Value</li>
</ol>
<p>Dalam kasus ini kita akan menangani missing value dengan dua cara, yaitu</p>
<ol style="list-style-type: decimal">
<li>Mereplace missing value pada kolom-kolom yang memiliki banyak sekali missing value (diatas 500)</li>
<li>Menghapus baris-baris yang mengandung missing value pada kolom-kolom yang memiliki sedikti missing value (dibawah 500)</li>
</ol>
<p>Berikut dibawah ini adalah sintaks untuk melakukan replace missing value, khususnya jika datanya berupa <code>factor</code> atau <code>string</code>. Kemudian <code>na.omit</code> digunakan untuk menghapus semua baris yang mengandung missing value</p>
<!-- rnb-text-end -->
<!-- rnb-chunk-begin -->
<!-- rnb-source-begin  -->
<pre class="r"><code>data_house1 &lt;- data_house %&gt;%
  select(-Id) %&gt;% 
  mutate(
    Alley = forcats::fct_explicit_na(Alley, na_level = &quot;Ukn&quot;),
    FireplaceQu=forcats::fct_explicit_na(FireplaceQu,
                                      na_level = &quot;Ukn&quot;   
                                         ),
    PoolQC = forcats::fct_explicit_na(PoolQC, na_level = &quot;Ukn&quot;),
    Fence = forcats::fct_explicit_na(Fence, na_level = &quot;Ukn&quot;),
    MiscFeature = forcats::fct_explicit_na(MiscFeature, na_level = &quot;Ukn&quot;)
  ) %&gt;% na.omit</code></pre>
<!-- rnb-source-end -->
<!-- rnb-chunk-end -->
<!-- rnb-text-begin -->

<pre class="r"><code>cor_mat &lt;- cor(data_house1%&gt;%
                   select_if(is.numeric),method = &quot;spearman&quot;)
cor_mat[upper.tri(cor_mat,diag = TRUE)] &lt;- NA 
cor_df &lt;- cor_mat   %&gt;%
    as.data.frame() %&gt;% 
    rownames_to_column(var = &quot;Var1&quot;) %&gt;%
  pivot_longer(names_to = &quot;Var2&quot;,
               values_to = &quot;corr&quot;,
               -Var1) %&gt;% na.omit

cor_df %&gt;% filter(abs(corr)&gt;0.6) %&gt;% arrange(desc(abs(corr)))</code></pre>

$(document).ready(function () {
  $('.knitsql-table').addClass('kable-table');
  var container = $('.kable-table');
  container.each(function() {

    caption.insertBefore($(this)).css('display', 'inherit');
  });
});
